<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 21:07:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>欧盟贸易组织长期负责人离开中国表示投资者仍然热衷，但持更多保留态度</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252119/leaving-china-long-time-eu-trade-group-chief-says-investors-remain-keen-more-reservations?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国欧盟商会名誉会长伍特克表示，跨国公司仍然希望投资，但障碍包括制造业产能过剩和高层领导层缺乏坦诚。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252119/leaving-china-long-time-eu-trade-group-chief-says-investors-remain-keen-more-reservations?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“涉及中国游客的事故”后，中国警告在巴厘岛度假的国民注意安全风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252110/china-warns-nationals-holidaying-bali-mind-safety-risks-after-accidents-involving-chinese-tourists?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>驻登巴萨总领馆在微信帖子中提醒中国公民不要骑无证滑板车，并注意山路和水中的风险，但数小时内删除了有关致命事故的内容。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 14:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252110/china-warns-nationals-holidaying-bali-mind-safety-risks-after-accidents-involving-chinese-tourists?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国正在向欧洲和亚洲开放免签规则。为什么日本和英国没有晋级？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251442/china-opening-visa-free-rules-europe-and-asia-why-have-japan-and-uk-not-made-cut?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>观察人士表示，将经济强国日本和英国排除在外，表明中国在寻求提振后疫情时代经济的同时，仍然注重地缘政治考虑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251442/china-opening-visa-free-rules-europe-and-asia-why-have-japan-and-uk-not-made-cut?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>春节旅游高峰期间，前往热门海岛度假胜地海南的中国游客遭遇返程机票短缺</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252098/chinese-tourists-visiting-popular-island-resort-hainan-caught-out-return-ticket-shortages-amid-lunar?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于一时兴起前往这个热带岛屿的旅客发现自己因缺票而陷入困境，航空当局希望增加航班。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252098/chinese-tourists-visiting-popular-island-resort-hainan-caught-out-return-ticket-shortages-amid-lunar?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>与美国不同，中国股市无需担心特朗普当选总统</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/united-states/article/3252018/chinas-stock-market-has-little-fear-trump-presidency-unlike-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普将中国股市的下跌归功，但事实是，中国的国内因素而非外部因素在发挥作用。相反，重点应该放在特朗普连任后对美国民主、法治和美国经济政策可信度的威胁上。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/united-states/article/3252018/chinas-stock-market-has-little-fear-trump-presidency-unlike-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国王毅将在慕尼黑安全会议上倡导“平等有序的多极世界”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252075/chinas-wang-yi-champion-equal-and-orderly-multipolar-world-munich-security-conference?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>最高外交官王毅将参加在德国举行的被称为“国防达沃斯”的年度会议，该会议可能会讨论中东和乌克兰的战争问题。在欧洲期间，中国外长还将访问西班牙和法国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 10:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252075/chinas-wang-yi-champion-equal-and-orderly-multipolar-world-munich-security-conference?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为遏制农历新年经济低迷，上海雇佣飞机、火车和汽车接工人回家</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252079/shanghai-hires-planes-trains-and-automobiles-bring-workers-back-and-curb-lunar-new-year-lull?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>为期一周的假期使得维持生产水平变得更加困难，因为各省市正面临着加速中国经济引擎的压力，加剧了对劳动力资源的竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252079/shanghai-hires-planes-trains-and-automobiles-bring-workers-back-and-curb-lunar-new-year-lull?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>Rokid 首席执行官表示，苹果的 Vision Pro 引发了人们对扩展现实技术的兴趣，刺激了对更实惠的耳机的更广泛需求</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252013/apples-vision-pro-raises-interest-extended-reality-technology-spurring-broader-demand-more?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>Rokid首席执行官Misa Zhu Mingming表示，苹果的Vision Pro耳机预计将刺激对更实惠且符合人体工程学设计的AR和VR可穿戴设备的更广泛需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252013/apples-vision-pro-raises-interest-extended-reality-technology-spurring-broader-demand-more?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国团队测试肺部治疗方法，这可能是第一个扭转影响7亿人的慢性疾病损害的方法</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252047/chinese-team-tests-lung-treatment-may-be-first-reverse-damage-chronic-disease-affecting-700-million?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该论文遵循左伟的说法，“基于干细胞和祖细胞的再生医学可能是治愈慢性阻塞性肺病的最大希望，即使不是唯一希望”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 07:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252047/chinese-team-tests-lung-treatment-may-be-first-reverse-damage-chronic-disease-affecting-700-million?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中澳关系：一旦北京取消进口关税，Treasury Wine 准备运送奔富 (Penfolds) 和 Icon 酒瓶</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252025/china-australia-relations-treasury-wine-readies-ship-penfolds-icon-bottles-once-beijing-lifts-import?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国正在审查对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税，人们普遍预期下个月将取消关税，富邑葡萄酒庄园计划从其他全球市场重新分配库存。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252025/china-australia-relations-treasury-wine-readies-ship-penfolds-icon-bottles-once-beijing-lifts-import?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中美科技战：荷兰芯片工具巨头ASML表示地缘政治、新的出口限制仍然存在风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3252010/us-china-tech-war-dutch-chip-tool-giant-asml-says-geopolitics-new-export-curbs-remain-risks?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该公司表示，“在地缘政治背景下自给自足的雄心所驱动”，它面临着来自竞争对手公司的新竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 03:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-war/article/3252010/us-china-tech-war-dutch-chip-tool-giant-asml-says-geopolitics-new-export-curbs-remain-risks?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>在遭受重创的中国股市中，交易员青睐“彩票”交易</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3252006/battered-chinese-stocks-traders-favour-lottery-ticket-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国股市崩盘的废墟中，华尔街交易员押注北京官员能够推动经济复苏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 02:46:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3252006/battered-chinese-stocks-traders-favour-lottery-ticket-trade?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着经济放缓，中国年轻人“躺平”，“空闲时间价值超过数千元”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251997/chinas-youth-lie-flat-economy-slows-free-time-worth-more-several-thousand-yuan?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国的青年失业率在六月份升至历史新高，经济仍在努力恢复到大流行前的增长水平，一些人现在的工作量只够他们花时间做自己喜欢的事情。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 02:05:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3251997/chinas-youth-lie-flat-economy-slows-free-time-worth-more-several-thousand-yuan?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国农历新年烟花爆竹：再受欢迎的传统也不能忽视公共安全</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3251833/chinas-lunar-new-year-fireworks-even-beloved-tradition-cant-ignore-public-safety?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>每到过年，关于禁燃烟花爆竹庆祝新年的争论就会重新出现。应该取得平衡，地方政府有余地制定适合情况的法规。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 01:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3251833/chinas-lunar-new-year-fireworks-even-beloved-tradition-cant-ignore-public-safety?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>想要在发短信时添加表情符号吗？英国研究人员表示，请三思，因为背景很重要</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251966/thinking-adding-smiley-you-text-think-again-say-researchers-britain-context-matters?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>诺丁汉大学的研究人员在《PLOS ONE》杂志上发表的一项针对英国和中国成年人的研究中表示，年龄、文化背景和性别会影响人们解读表情符号的方式。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251966/thinking-adding-smiley-you-text-think-again-say-researchers-britain-context-matters?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>